title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Daily 4' game
maintext:
SACRAMENTO (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday evening’s drawing of the California Lottery’s “Daily 4” game were:
2-7-2-9
(two, seven, two, nine)
¶ Ticket-holders with all four winning numbers in the order given win the top prize. Lesser amounts are also awarded to ticket-holders with other varying combinations of the winning numbers.
